<dl id="n40029b"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n40" href="#n40029b">N40 (VI.B.28B)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n40all.htm#n40029b"> 29(b)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> bullockbandy</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Driving along in our bullock-bandy a month or two later we observe a number of women at work in a wide-stretching field. The sun shineth in his strength, but the good Travancore breeze mitigates his ferocity. <small> Rev W.S. Hunt, <a name="WSHI1" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#WSHI1"><cite title="source">India's Outcastes: A New Era</cite></a> (1924) 31</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
